"{\"uid\": \"chronofhorse.com-article-in-photos-olympic-eventers-on-form-at-mandatory-outing\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Saturday, Dec. 6, 2025 The horse-and-rider combinations named as members or alternates for the U.S. Eventing Team headed to the Paris Olympic Games went for style and confidence rather than speed at their mandatory outing over the weekend, and with the exception of one fall cross-country, all went to plan.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 101, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1807638637537354e-40, \"text\": \"Eventing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday, Dec.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"The horse-and-rider combinations\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 55}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"alternates\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 86}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 147}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 162}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"their mandatory outing\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"the exception\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"one fall cross\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The advanced division at the June Stable View Horse Trials, held June 22-23 in Aiken, South Carolina, served as the final Olympic preparation event for the pairs, which included the named team-Will Coleman with Off The Record and his direct reserve Diabolo, Boyd Martin with Fedarman B and his direct reserve Commando 3, and Caroline Pamukcu and HSH Blake-as well as traveling alternate Liz Halliday and Cooley Nutcracker and six more non-traveling reserve pairs.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aiken, South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aiken, South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aiken,_South_Carolina\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\", \"score\": 0.999960588638654, \"rank\": 2.1642501072871448e-05, \"text\": \"Coleman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\"}, {\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9288909289526298, \"rank\": 0.07655265701651054, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.999772578184827, \"rank\": 0.00012452923161572222, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\"}, {\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liz_Halliday-Sharp\", \"s